Plintissa was floating free, seperated from Artist when he had died. Sudden=
ly, in the middle of a happy thought, she was jerked down and felt like a t=
rain hit her. Then she woke up and looked up. Deemos was standing there, sm=
iling, and holding something. Plintissa realized she was alive again, and p=
laced back into the world she hated so much, placed back in the world where=
 everyone treated her like she didn't exist, and placed in a world without =
anyone who loved her. Plintissa instantly tried to kill herself, but was pr=
evented and shocked hard.

"You are foolish, I have complete control over y=
ou, you cannot resist me now!" Deemos laughed and pressed a button. Plintis=
sa was forced to stand up from multiple shocks.

"You feel pain should you =
not obey my brain waves, sweetheart! Don't worry, your boyfriend won't be p=
ainting pictures anymore, but there's still plenty of him to go around." De=
emos said. He held up another remore control, the one he was controlling Ga=
ngon with.

"2 new members, it just keeps getting better!" Deemos laughs an=
d walks back toward the Maximal base. Plintissa stands there, horrified by =
all of this. Deemos comes back and drags her with him. She takes a swing at=
 him and only hurts herself.

"I was too smart for that, don' be stupid!" D=
eemos says. He smiles again and drags Plintissa back to the Maximal base...=
